{"tid":1349941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勿信謠言 堅持五大訴求 堅守原則","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:46:03.000Z","uid":147376,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"55df5e2f868bbc1e0e93a1e7739ae1c08db35ee2","tid":1349941,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>小心，政府係想市民恐慌，令大家唔再團結，人人自危，人鬼難分<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好信咩傳言話幾點邊度會黑社會...製造恐慌，錯導民意<br />\n<br />\n以後嘅日子，我哋要集中：<br />\n(堅持五大訴求)<br />\n1.全面撤回送中惡法，永不重提<br />\n2.成立獨立調查委員會，徹查警方濫權及警黑勾結<br />\n3.收回暴動定性<br />\n4.撤銷示威者控罪<br />\n5.雙普選<br />\n<br />\n(加強地區工作)目標為連結街頭抗爭同普通市民<br />\n1.派傳單<br />\n2.網上文宣，可利用fb,ig,airdrop散播<br />\n<br />\n(持續給予政府壓力)<br />\n1.目標清晰嘅遊行，示威，集會<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"598df5a6ef229bb68b9be775a00a755bb3847914","tid":1349941,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:33:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4333b5a78cbc5f7ece67a11d2e17e8d5b549673","tid":1349941,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83d06b712379936049138d7d7bb1ecc0ab512d07","tid":1349941,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a0ad31d65df177278cb72370328cafc028ff6bd","tid":1349941,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:39:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66ec6c56de91aecc49c16bf73b13400d61ff5764","tid":1349941,"uid":220144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:23:38.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"1406eec79846f690ba581fd4a500d52ae0243421","tid":1349941,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:26:09.000Z","msg":"我宣布「政警鄉黑」大合作，「黑警、黑鄉、黑社會」合稱「三黑」，必須追究「三黑」暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1339336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1339336</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"063d5e22